Currently, attachments can only be visible within Customer Portal only if it was attached during ticket creation, comment / add attachment functionality by a client, or attached and then added to comment via a wiki markup link by an agent.

In the event of a trac import, even if there are attachments included in the import, it does not generate comments for the attachments, hence leading the attachments to not be visible to the customers in the portal. 

The trac import process should know this restriction, and have created the comments accordingly, so that the service desk users can see the attachments.

